cdata.name: CyClean
cdata.desc:
CyClean is an electric vehicle rental platform. CyClean hasdeveloped a tokenized ecosystem where users are able to rent electric vehicles and mine the platform native tokens (CCL) while doing so. CyClean uses a wireless system in order to report the usage of Metter/Watts of its products. The use of this mining mechanism allows the platform to bring together the blockchain technology with a green solution for individual transportation.

The CCL token is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is the platform's utility token and it will serve the users as a mediumof exchange as well as to reward them when mining by circulating with the platformavailableelectric vehicles.
